  <FCP_Backstory_PRC_Army_Battlefield_Medic.title>戰地醫療兵</FCP_Backstory_PRC_Army_Battlefield_Medic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_PRC_Army_Battlefield_Medic.titleShort>軍醫</FCP_Backstory_PRC_Army_Battlefield_Medic.titleShort>
