  <FCP_Backstory_PRC_Army_ChemicalWarfare_Trooper.title>化學戰士兵</FCP_Backstory_PRC_Army_ChemicalWarfare_Trooper.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_PRC_Army_ChemicalWarfare_Trooper.titleShort>化學士兵</FCP_Backstory_PRC_Army_ChemicalWarfare_Trooper.titleShort>
